            <p>
                We do not sell, trade, or otherwise transfer your personal information to third parties without your
                consent, except as described in this policy. We may share information with:
            </p>
            <ul>
                <li>Course instructors (limited to course-related data)</li>
                <li>Service providers who assist us in operating our platform</li>
                <li>Legal authorities when required by law</li>

                <li>Business partners for educational collaborations (with your consent)</li>

        </div>

        <div class="privacy-section">
            <h3><i class="fas fa-shield-alt me-2"></i>Data Security</h3>
